Bishii Maarso 11, Ra'iisul Wasaare Conte wuxuu amray in la joojiyo waxqabadyada ganacsiga oo dhan marka laga reebo dukaamada waaweyn iyo farmashiyaha. Bishii Maarso 6, Kolejiyadda Talyaaniga ee Anesthesia, Analgesia, Reanimation and Intensive Care (SIAARTI) ayaa daabacay talooyin ku saabsan anshaxa caafimaadka ee ku saabsan borotokoollada kala soocida ee la isticmaali karo.
