Tijaabooyinka shaybaarka ee cudurka neefsashada ee coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) iyo fayraska SARS-CoV-2 ee la xiriira waxaa ka mid ah habab lagu ogaado jiritaanka fayraska iyo kuwa lagu ogaado jirka ka hortagga cudurka.
Joogitaanka fayraska ee shaybaarka waxaa lagu xaqiijiyay tijaabada isku dhafka ee polymerase-ka ee transcriptase-ka soo noqnoqda, taas oo ogaanaysa RNA-ga coronavirus.
Tijaabadan waa mid gaar ah waxaana loogu talagalay in lagu ogaado RNA-ga fayraska SARS-CoV-2 oo keliya.
Waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu xaqiijiyo cudurrada dhawaan ama kuwa dhawaan jira.
Xogta antibody (serology) waxaa loo isticmaali karaa labadaba baaritaanka iyo kormeerka dadka.
Tijaabada antibody-yada waxay muujinayaan inta qof ee qaba cudurka, oo ay ku jiraan kuwa qaba astaamo aad u fudud si aan loo soo sheegin ama aan lahayn astaamo.
Natiijada baaritaankaas ayaa lagu ogaan karaa heerka dhimashada cudurka iyo heerka difaaca guud ee dadka.
Tijaabooyinka xaddidan awgood, ilaa Maarso 2020, ma jirin dal xog lagu kalsoonaan karo ku saabsan faafitaanka fayraska dadka.
Ilaa 23 March, ma jirin dal tijaabiyay in ka badan 3% dadka, waxaana jira isbeddel weyn tirada tijaabada ee lagu sameeyay dalalka kala duwan.
Isbeddelkaasi wuxuu sidoo kale u badan yahay inuu saameyn weyn ku yeesho heerarka dhimashada ee kiisaska la soo sheegay, kuwaas oo laga yaabo inay aad ugu xad dhaafsan yihiin dalalka qaarkood.
Iyada oo loo marayo isku dhafka polymerase ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee transcriptase-ka (rRT-PCR), baaritaanka waxaa lagu sameyn karaa muunado neefsashada oo lagu soo saaray habab kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan isopate nasopharynx ama muunado aflagaado.
Natiijooyinka waxaa caadi ahaan la heli karaa saacado yar ilaa 2 maalmood.
Tijaabada isku dhafka ee polymerase-ka ee transcriptase-ka-dhaafka ah ee lagu sameeyay isopate-yada faringees waa mid lagu kalsoonaan karo oo keliya usbuuca ugu horreeya ee cudurka.
Kadib, fayraska ayaa laga yaabaa inuu ka baxo qoorta, laakiin wuxuu sii kordhayaa sanbabada.
Dadka qaba cudurka ee la tijaabiyo usbuuca labaad, haddii kale, shaybaarka waxaa laga heli karaa qaybaha qoto dheer ee hawada iyada oo loo marayo catheter nuugista, ama waxaa loo isticmaali karaa shaybaarka lagu tuuro qallajinta (dhibcaha).
Tijaabada ugu horreysa ee isku dhafka isku dhafka ee polymerase ayaa lagu sameeyay Charité, Berlin bishii Janaayo 2020, iyadoo la adeegsanayo isku dhafka isku dhafka ee polymerase ee leh transcriptase-ka dib-u-dhaca waqtiga dhabta ah (rRT-PCR), waxayna aasaas u ahayd 250 000 xirmo oo ay qaybisay Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO).
Bishii Janaayo 23, 2020, Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa sidoo kale horumarisay tijaabo. Bishii Janaayo 28, 2020, shirkadda Koonfurta Kuuriya ee Kogenebiotech waxay horumarisay qalab lagu ogaado SARS-CoV-2 oo ku saleysan falcelinta silsiladda ee heerka caafimaad ee polymerase (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Waxay raadineysaa gen "E" oo ay wadaagaan dhammaan betacoronavirus iyo SARS-CoV-2 gaar ah ee gen RdRp. Shiinaha, BGI Group waxay ka mid ahayd shirkadaha ugu horreeya ee helaya oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah ee Maamulka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ee alaabada caafimaadka ee SARS-CoV-2 qalab lagu ogaado oo ku saleysan falcelinta silsiladda ee polymerase. Mareykanka, Xarumaha Xakamaynta iyo Ka Hortagga Cudurrada (CDC) waxay u qaybiyaan guddigooda baaritaanka falcelinta silsiladda ee polymerase ee la adeegsanayo transcriptase-ka dhabta ah ee coronavirus cusub 2019 (2019-nCoV) shaybaarada caafimaadka dadweynaha iyada oo loo marayo International Reagent Resource.
