Sidoo kale, 9kii Maarso 2020, Quest Diagnostics waxay diyaar u noqotay tijaabooyinka COVID-19 heer qaran.
Wax xad ah oo tirada ah lama sheegin; soo-saarka shaybaarka iyo ka shaqeynta waa in la sameeyaa iyadoo la raacayo shuruudaha CDC.
Ruushka, tijaabada COVID-19 waxaa soo saaray oo soo saaray Xarunta Cilmi-baarista ee Virology iyo Biotechnology ee VECTOR.
Bishii Febraayo 11, 2020, tijaabada waxaa diiwaangeliyey Adeegga Federaalka ee Kormeerka Daryeelka Caafimaadka. Bishii Maarso 12, 2020, waxaa la sheegay in Mayo Clinic ay soo saartay tijaabada lagu ogaanayo cudurka COVID-19. Bishii Maarso 13, 2020, Roche Diagnostics waxay heshay oggolaanshaha FDA ee tijaabada lagu sameyn karo 3.5 saacadood gudahood mug weyn, taas oo u oggolaaneysa mashiinka inuu sameeyo qiyaastii 4128 tijaabooyin 24 saacadood gudahood.
Bishii Maarso 19, 2020, FDA waxay oggolaansho u soo saartay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee Abbott Laboratories tijaabo ku saabsan Abbott m2000 nidaamka; FDA waxay horay u soo saartay oggolaansho la mid ah Hologic, LabCorp iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Bishii Maarso 21, 2020, Cepheid ayaa sidoo kale heshay oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah ee FDA tijaabada oo qaadata qiyaastii 45 daqiiqo.
FDA waxay ansixisay tijaabo isticmaaleysa tikniyoolajiyadda isothermal amplification ee nucleic acids halkii ay ka isticmaali lahayd falcelinta silsiladda ee polymerase.
Maadaama aysan u baahnayn in la sameeyo wareegyo heerkul ah oo kala duwan, habkan wuxuu ku siin karaa natiijooyin wanaagsan shan daqiiqo gudahood iyo natiijooyin taban 13 daqiiqo gudahood.
Hada waxaa jira 18,000 oo mashiin oo noocan ah oo ku yaal Mareykanka, Abbott waxay qorsheyneysaa inay kordhiso wax soo saarka si ay u sameyso 50,000 baaritaan maalin kasta. Taiwan, waxaa lagu horumarinayaa tijaabo isticmaalaya antibody monoclonal oo si gaar ah ugu xidhaya borotiinka nucleocapside (protein N) ee coronavirus-ka cusub, iyadoo la rajeynayo inay natiijooyin ku siin karto 15 ilaa 20 daqiiqo gudahood sida tijaabo degdeg ah oo loogu talagalay hargabka.
Bishii Maarso 2020, dib u eegista daabacaadaha ayaa lagu soo gabagabeeyay in "Xirinta Xarkaha Qolofta ay leedahay qiimo yar oo lagu ogaado marxaladaha hore, halka natiijooyinka CT [tomography kombuyuutarka] la heli karo xitaa ka hor inta aan calaamadaha soo muuqan".
Tilmaamaha caadiga ah ee TC waxaa ka mid ah dhalooyinka dhalooyinka badan ee dhalooyinka leh ee galaas la duubay oo leh qaybinta hareeraha, isugeynta iyo gadaal.
