Bishii Maarso 16, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa dalbaday in la kordhiyo barnaamijyada tijaabada sida habka ugu wanaagsan ee loo yareeyo horumarka cudurka faafa ee COVID-19. Baahida sare ee tijaabada sababtoo ah faafitaanka ballaaran ee fayraska ayaa sababay dib u dhac boqolaal kun oo tijaabada ah ee shaybaarada gaarka loo leeyahay ee Mareykanka, iyo sahayda hiisopate iyo kiimikooyinka kiimikada ayaa dhammaaday.
Bishii Maarso ee sannadkii 2020, Shiinaha ayaa soo sheegay dhibaatooyin ku saabsan saxnaanta qalabka tijaabada.
Mareykanka, qalabka tijaabada ee ay soo saareen CDC waxay lahaayeen "caqabado"; Dowladdu waxay ka takhalusatay caqabadaha dawliga ah ee ka hortagga tijaabada gaarka loo leeyahay. Spain waxay ka iibsatay qalabka tijaabada shirkadda Shiinaha ee Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Co Ltd, laakiin waxay heshay natiijooyin aan sax ahayn.
