Shaqooyinka khatarta sare leh ee soo bandhigida waxaa ka mid ah kuwa ka shaqeeya adeegyada gaarsiinta, taageerada, shaybaarka iyo gaadiidka caafimaadka ee la soo bandhigay bukaanka la xaqiijiyey ama la shakiyay COVID-19.
Shaqooyinkan waxay noqdaan shaqooyin khatar badan leh haddii shaqaalaha ay sameeyaan hababka soo saarista aerosols bukaanka la xaqiijiyey ama laga shakisan yahay COVID-19 ama haddii ay qaataan ama wax ka qabtaan shaybaarka bukaankaas.
Hababka soo saarista hawada waxaa ka mid ah qanjirka, nidaamyada qandho-gelinta, bronchoscopy, qaar ka mid ah nidaamyada iyo baaritaannada ilkaha ama qaadashada shaybaarka.
Shaqooyinka masaajidka ee khatarta sare leh ee soo bandhigida waxaa ka mid ah kuwa shaqaalaha ku lug leh diyaarinta meydadka dadka qaba COVID-19 ama la tuhmay inay ku yeelan karaan dhimashada; kuwaas oo leh halis aad u sarreeya oo soo bandhigida haddii la sameeyo gawaarida la dilay.
